<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="harm-n">harm <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /hɑːm/    美 /hɑːrm/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>伤害；损害；危害：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He may not be able to help but <strong>there's no harm in</strong> asking him.
他可能帮不上忙，但是问他一下倒也无妨。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="do-harm-to-do-harm">do harm to / do ... harm</h3>
<p>1.<strong>伤害；对…有害：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Too much drinking will do great harm to you. / Too much drinking will do you great harm.
饮酒过量危害甚大。</p></div></div>